Our Residential Earthquake Insurance Policies
Whether you own a house, mobilehome or condo unit, or you rent, California Earthquake Authority (CEA) has an earthquake insurance policy that gives you the strength to rebuild and recover. With more coverage choices, more deductible options and more affordable rates,  you now have the flexibility to find a policy that fits your needs and your budget.​
Choose the residential earthquake policy you're looking for:


Homeowners


Condo Unit Owners


Mobilehome Owners


Renters


How Do I Buy an Earthquake Insurance Policy or Change My Coverage? And What's My Risk?


Learn the facts about California earthquakes, your risk, and how to get prepared.


Select the CEA earthquake insurance coverage that meets your needs and budget.


Contact your home insurance company to buy a CEA policy or make changes to your coverage.






















